---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import BackHome from "../components/BackHome.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <main class="min-h-screen px-6 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <BackHome />

      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-50">
        About
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">

        <p>
          I work across real estate development, construction, operations, and technology.
          My background includes hands-on project delivery, asset management, and operational
          leadership, with a focus on building systems (both physical and digital) that
          create effective, accessible environments.
        </p>

        <p>
          This site is a personal home for links,
          <a href="/posts" class="font-medium text-orange-300 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-orange-400/30 transition-colors duration-150 hover:text-orange-400 hover:decoration-orange-400/60">occasional writing</a>
          , and
          <a href="/resources" class="font-medium text-orange-300 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-orange-400/30 transition-colors duration-150 hover:text-orange-400 hover:decoration-orange-400/60">resources</a>
          I’ve created. It’s a place to share ideas, tools, and notes that may be useful to others.
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

